OL,3,CFans 'bombarded' with gambling
OL,4,Cmessages during Premier League
OL,6,FFootball fans have been "bombarded"
OL,7,Fwith gambling adverts during this
OL,8,Fseason's Premier League, according to
OL,9,Fnew research.
OL,11,FA University of Bristol study recorded
OL,12,Fmore than 27,000 gambling messages
OL,13,Facross the opening weekend of the
OL,14,Ffootball tournament - almost three
OL,15,Ftimes higher than in 2023.
OL,17,FThe adverts were observed across TV,
OL,18,Fradio and social media, with logos
OL,19,Fseen on hoardings, football shirts and
OL,20,Fstadium structures.
