OL,6,FDuring the match between Wolverhampton
OL,7,Fand Manchester City, gambling adverts
OL,8,Fand logos were at their highest,
OL,9,Ftotalling 5,262 - an average of 22 per
OL,10,Fminute.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe report's authors suggest the
OL,18,Ffindings point towards a "broken
OL,19,Fsystem," with a patchwork of
OL,20,Fregulation and voluntary industry
OL,21,Fcodes.
