OL,4,Cmessages during Premier League
OL,6,FIn 2019, gambling companies agreed to
OL,7,Fa self-regulated "whistle-to-whistle"
OL,8,Fban, meaning that TV betting adverts
OL,9,Fare not shown between five minutes
OL,10,Fbefore kick-off and five minutes after
OL,11,Ffull-time. It does not cover logos on
OL,12,Fphysical spaces like pitchside
OL,13,Felectronic signs.
OL,15,FIn the opening round this season,
OL,16,Fresearchers found that there were more
OL,17,Fthan 13,000 gambling messages in the
OL,18,FUK during this restricted period - an
OL,19,Fincrease of 32% on the year before.
