OL,6,FProject lead Dr Raffaello Rossi said
OL,7,Fthat the league is now so "saturated"
OL,8,Fwith marketing that brands are
OL,9,Ffighting each other for every inch of
OL,10,Fadvertising space.
OL,12,F"The evidence is now overwhelming:
OL,13,Fself-regulation has failed. Voluntary
OL,14,Fcodes are protecting profits, not
OL,15,Ffans," he said.
OL,17,F"The question now is how much more
OL,18,Fevidence the government needs before
OL,19,Fit finally steps in to act."
