OL,6,FThose who have had their lives
OL,7,Fimpacted by the effects of gambling
OL,8,Faddiction are also calling for more to
OL,9,Fbe done to safeguard those who are
OL,10,Fvulnerable.
OL,12,FMartin Jones' son Joshua was a 23-year-
OL,13,Fold graduate accountant who became
OL,14,Faddicted to online poker and betting.
OL,15,FHe died by suicide in August 2015.
OL,17,FResponding to the findings, Martin
OL,18,Fsaid he was "staggered that the amount
OL,19,Fof harm is virtually unchanged" since
OL,20,FJosh's death.
