OL,6,FSir Iain Duncan Smith MP, the chair of
OL,7,Fthe Gambling Reform All Party
OL,8,FParliamentary Group, also described
OL,9,Fthe findings as "astonishing,"
OL,10,Falthough the overall number of
OL,11,Fgambling messages recorded during the
OL,12,Fopening weekend fell slightly when
OL,13,Fcompared with last year.
OL,15,FThe study uncovered widespread
OL,16,Fpromotion by unlicensed operators.
OL,17,FAround one in ten gambling ads came
OL,18,Ffrom companies without a UK licence,
OL,19,Fwhich the report says is an apparent
OL,20,Fbreach of the industry's Sponsorship
OL,21,FCode of Conduct introduced in 2024.
