OL,6,FA ban on gambling sponsors appearing
OL,7,Fon the front of Premier League shirts
OL,8,Fis set to start from the 2026-2027
OL,9,Fseason as a voluntary club decision,
OL,10,Falthough some have described the move
OL,11,Fas tokenistic, as gambling logos will
OL,12,Fstill be allowed on shirt sleeves and
OL,13,Ftraining kits.
OL,15,FJust over half of the clubs in the
OL,16,Fleague started the season sporting
OL,17,Fgambling sponsors, although the
OL,18,FPremier League itself does not have a
OL,19,Fbetting partner.
