OL,6,FThe findings also suggest that social
OL,7,Fmedia gambling adverts generated more
OL,8,Fthan 34 million views across the
OL,9,Fopening weekend.
OL,11,FThe Betting and Gaming Council (BGC) -
OL,12,Fthe industry standards body - pointed
OL,13,Fout that "betting advertising and
OL,14,Fsponsorship must comply with strict
OL,15,Fguidelines and safer gambling tools
OL,16,Fand signposts to help for those
OL,17,Fconcerned about their betting are
OL,18,Fregularly and prominently displayed.
